* Notification\nDestinations
** Email
***_ Direct email address
***_ No admin setup needed
** System Destinations
*** Slack
****_ Channel notifications
****_ Team visibility
*** Microsoft Teams
****_ Collaboration platform
*** PagerDuty
****_ On-call escalation
****_ Incident management
*** HTTP Webhooks
****_ Custom integrations
****_ Any HTTP endpoint
** Admin Setup
***_ Admin Settings > Notifications
***_ Configure per destination type
***_ Up to 3 destinations per event type
